high_descs: Step forward, then turn left to face the counter near the dishwasher.
Pick up the lettuce nearest to you from the counter.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the lettuce inside and chill it, then take the lettuce out.
Turn right and move forward, then turn left at the dishwasher.
Place the lettuce on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce on the counter.
